-size-1.avif" loading=3D"lazy" alt=3D"how to calculate sample size for know=
n population"></div></figure><h4><strong><em>Sample size for unknown popula=
tion</em></strong></h4><figure style=3D"max-width:1110px" class=3D"w-richte=
xt-align-fullwidth w-richtext-figure-type-image"><div><img src=3D"https://c=
